1- First setup

mkdir FLASKAPP
cd FLASKAPP
python3 -m venv env
source ./env/bin/active
touch requirement.txt
nano requirement.txt 
write all dependence neccessary for development
pip install -r requirement.txt

2- Second setup
generate template for flask app
create *template folder in racing project
cd template
create all vue for render template
create a view *base.html fix for all views
create folder partials
cd partials
touch _navbar.html

3- Third setup (deployment on heroku)
login heroku
heroku create pcoder-flask-mini-crud
git push heroku master
link web site: https://pcoder-flask-mini-crud.herokuapp.com/
repository heroku: https://git.heroku.com/pcoder-flask-mini-crud.git

----------Launcher project flask app
flask --app <name_app> --debug run


------------    gitlab      ------------
cd existing_repo
git remote add origin https://gitlab.com/Guy-Sylvestre/flask-mini-crud.git
git branch -M main



----------      heroku      --------------
git remote add origin https://git.heroku.com/pcoder-flask-mini-crud.git
git branch -M master
git push -uf origin main